          h1 the cusine
          p At the cross of where tradition meets innovation, we have developed our menu. Taking the best from Maine's land, sea and soil, our chef Jason Paul has embarked on a culinary journey highlighting the best from what's in season. Inspired by the local flora and fauna, we present cuisine that will indulge the senses and nourish the body.
